{"type":"text","timestamp":1783489115149,"sessionID":"ses_0bfc4afb7ffeA8X2g5OnaG20YL","part":{"id":"prt_f403c2f7c0015GKjTZs8g8A4ol","messageID":"msg_f403c0e1d001RY0HFhGtfjyZNG","sessionID":"ses_0bfc4afb7ffeA8X2g5OnaG20YL","type":"text","text":"The contract says the command/YAML owns state, dispatch, convergence, and synthesis, but this detached lineage request overrides artifact resolution and constrains writes to the lineage directory. I’ll load the loop/state/convergence references, then initialize and run the file-backed lineage within that boundary.","time":{"start":1783489113980,"end":1783489115147},"metadata":{"openai":{"itemId":"msg_080d7e264695dcb3016a4de259f7ac81918229c067b1660c53","phase":"commentary"}}}}
