time`, so they share a state format, a stop contract and a coverage model. The improvement family alone carries four co-equal lanes (agent improvement, model benchmark, skill benchmark, non-dev AI system refine), giving eight `/deep:*` loop comman... (line truncated to 2000 chars)\n98: {\"type\":\"step_finish\",\"timestamp\":1783488085650,\"sessionID\":\"ses_0bfd72ffbffeOJIQWH3C696a5x\",\"part\":{\"id\":\"prt_f402c7e900014QlZr9LrAlLlNM\",\"reason\":\"tool-calls\",\"snapshot\":\"c353700800e9f55b88984f53ec57cb4488476fe5\",\"messageID\":\"msg_f402c4a45001Ho9Uqfq8omSvx9\",\"sessionID\":\"ses_0bfd72ffbffeOJIQWH3C696a5x\",\"type\":\"step-finish\",\"tokens\":{\"total\":192138,\"input\":18492,\"output\":563,\"reasoning\":27,\"cache\":{\"write\":0,\"read\":173056}},\"cost\":0}}\n99: {\"type\":\"step_start\",\"timestamp\":1783488087272,\"sessionID\":\"ses_0bfd72ffbffeOJIQWH3C696a5x\",\"part\":{\"id\":\"prt_f402c84e7001rjU1gSib1y0zqW\",\"messageID\":\"msg_f402c8001001AlIVs7PYaxdrb7\",\"sessionID\":\"ses_0bfd72ffbffeOJIQWH3C696a5x\",\"snapshot\":\"c353700800e9f55b88984f53ec57cb4488476fe5\",\"type\":\"step-start\"}}\n100: {\"type\":\"tool_use\",\"timestamp\":1783488095566,\"sessionID\":\"ses_0bfd72ffbffeOJIQWH3C696a5x\",\"part\":{\"type\":\"tool\",\"tool\":\"grep\",\"callID\":\"call_qBqkNRiMUsgmWjBeHRySZ5Wy\",\"state\":{\"status\":\"completed\",\"input\":{\"pattern\":\"MERGED_DEEP_SKILL_ID|MODE_REGISTRY_PATH|ALIASES_TS_PATH|deep-loop-workflows|deep-loop-runtime\",\"path\":\"/Users/michelkerkmeester/MEGA/Development/Code_Environment/Public/.opencode/skills/system-skill-advisor/mcp_server/scripts\",\"include\":\"*.py\"},\"output\":\"Found 28 matches\\n/Users/michelkerkmeester/MEGA/Development/Code_Environment/Public/.opencode/skills/system-skill-advisor/mcp_server/scripts/skill_advisor.py:\\n  Line 16:     --deep-skill-routing-json  Score deep-loop-workflows mode routing (research|review|ai-council) from JSON stdin\\n\\n  Line 83: MODE_REGISTRY_PATH = os.path.join(SKILLS_DIR, \\\"