n{\"type\":\"tool_use\",\"timestamp\":1783488085273,\"sessionID\":\"ses_0bfd72ffbffeOJIQWH3C696a5x\",\"part\":{\"type\":\"tool\",\"tool\":\"grep\",\"callID\":\"call_Gff38NZYgXRc86GPoXg6m99M\",\"state\":{\"status\":\"completed\",\"input\":{\"pattern\":\"deep-loop-workflows|deep-loop-runtime|system-deep-loop\",\"path\":\"/Users/michelkerkmeester/MEGA/Development/Code_Environment/Public/README.md\",\"include\":\"README.md\"},\"output\":\"Found 100 matches (more matches available)\\n/Users/michelkerkmeester/MEGA/Development/Code_Environment/Public/README.md:\\n  Line 192: This repo ships as a public template. Of the shipped skills, `sk-code` carries the stack-specific patterns (frontend framework, animation library, CMS, backend language). Start there when forking. The other shipped skills (`system-spec-kit`, `sk-doc`, `sk-git`, the `deep-loop-workflows` loops, `deep-loop-runtime`, the `cli-*` orchestrators) are codebase-agnostic out of the box and work for any project without modification. Most teams will also add their own skills on top. Drop them into `.opencode/skills/<your-skill>/` and they'll be picked up automatically.\\n\\n  Line 395: | **—**  | Moved Surfaces  | 0      | -            | Code graph → `mk_code_index`; advisor + skill graph → `mk_skill_advisor`; coverage + council graph → `deep-loop-runtime` CLI scripts (not MCP tools) |\\n\\n  Line 781: The Deep Loop system runs autonomous, iterative agent workflows. Each loop dispatches a fresh-context worker against externalized state, then keeps going until a convergence check, not the agent's own claim, decides a stop is safe. Five loop families (context, research, review, AI council, improvement) live as nested mode packets inside one parent skill, `deep-loop-workflows`, and all run on one shared runtime, `deep-loop-runtime`, so they share a state format, a stop contract and a coverage model. The improvement family alone carries four co-equal lanes (agent improvement, model benchmark, skill benchmark, non-dev AI system refine), giving eight `/deep:*` loop comman... (line truncated to 2000 chars)\n{\"type\":\"step_finish\",\"timestamp\":1783488085650,\"sessionID\":\"ses_0bfd72ffbffeOJIQWH3C696a5x\",\"part\":{\"id\":\"prt_f402c7e900014QlZr9LrAlLlNM\",\"reason\":\"tool-calls\",\"snapshot\":\"c353700800e9f55b88984f53ec57cb4488476fe5\",\"messageID\":\"msg_f402c4a45001Ho9Uqfq8omSvx9\",\"sessionID\":\"ses_0bfd72ffbffeOJIQWH3C696a5x\",\"type\":\"step-finish\",\"tokens\":{\"total\":192138,\"input\":18492,\"output\":563,\"reasoning\":27,\"cache\":{\"write\":0,\"read\":173056}},\"cost\":0}}\n{\"type\":\"step_start\",\"timestamp\":1783488087272,\"sessionID\":\"ses_0bfd72ffbffeOJIQWH3C696a5x\",\"part\":{\"id\":\"prt_f402c84e7001rjU1gSib1y0zqW\",\"messageID\":\"msg_f402c8001001AlIVs7PYaxdrb7\",\"sessionID\":\"ses_0bfd72ffbffeOJIQWH3C696a5x\",\"snapshot\":\"c353700800e9f55b88984f53ec57cb4488476fe5\",\"type\":\"step-start\"}}\n{\"type\":\"tool_use\",\"timestamp\":1783488095566,\"sessionID\":\"ses_0bfd72ffbffeOJIQWH3C696a5x\",\"part\":{\"type\":\"tool\",\"tool\":\"grep\",\"callID\":\"call_qBqkNRiMUsgmWjBeHRySZ5Wy\",\"state\":{\"status\":\"completed\",\"input\":{\"pattern\":\"MERGED_DEEP_SKILL_ID|MODE_REGISTRY_PATH|ALIASES_TS_PATH|deep-loop-workflows|deep-loop-runtime\",\"path\":\"/Users/michelkerkmeester/MEGA/Development/Code_Environment/Public/.opencode/skills/system-skill-advisor/mcp_server/scripts\",\"include\":\"*.py\"},\"output\":\"Found 28 matches\\n/Users/michelkerkmeester/MEGA/Development/Code_Environment/Public/.opencode/skills/system-skill-advisor/mcp_server/scripts/skill_advisor.py:\\n  Line 16:     --deep-skill-routing-json  Score deep-loop-workflows mode routing (research|review|ai-council) from JSON stdin\\n\\n  Line 83: MODE_REGISTRY_PATH = os.path.join(SKILLS_DIR, \\\"deep-loop-workflows\\\", \\\"mode-registry.json\\\")\\n\\n  Line 84: ALIASES_TS_PATH = os.path.join(\\n\\n  Line 315:     with open(MODE_REGISTRY_PATH, \\\"r\\\", encoding=\\\"utf-8\\\") as registry_file:\\