efs, and fallback-router status.\\n\\n### In Progress\\n- Convert gathered evidence into deep-research state/config/strategy/iteration artifacts inside the lineage directory.\\n\\n### Blocked\\n- `(none)`\\n\\n## Key Decisions\\n- Treat lineage as fresh; initialize new packet state rather than resume.\\n- Skip spec write-back/git staging unless explicitly allowed, because writes are constrained to the lineage directory.\\n-... (line truncated to 2000 chars)\n139: {\"type\":\"step_finish\",\"timestamp\":1783488222632,\"sessionID\":\"ses_0bfd72ffbffeOJIQWH3C696a5x\",\"part\":{\"id\":\"prt_f402e95a6001lGbKaYGEsjezAw\",\"reason\":\"stop\",\"snapshot\":\"9cb9852d8bfcfe7abb619e79af6e4ea65e914cef\",\"messageID\":\"msg_f402d58c9001b0UtMQfGhhF0OV\",\"sessionID\":\"ses_0bfd72ffbffeOJIQWH3C696a5x\",\"type\":\"step-finish\",\"tokens\":{\"total\":53681,\"input\":49301,\"output\":1274,\"reasoning\":3106,\"cache\":{\"write\":0,\"read\":0}},\"cost\":0}}\n140: {\"type\":\"text\",\"timestamp\":1783488223008,\"sessionID\":\"ses_0bfd72ffbffeOJIQWH3C696a5x\",\"part\":{\"id\":\"prt_f402e970b001WysR7KmJz3RIg9\",\"messageID\":\"msg_f402e970a0015Pzvf4wg7f6K6E\",\"sessionID\":\"ses_0bfd72ffbffeOJIQWH3C696a5x\",\"type\":\"text\",\"metadata\":{\"compaction_continue\":true},\"synthetic\":true,\"text\":\"Continue if you have next steps, or stop and ask for clarification if you are unsure how to proceed.\",\"time\":{\"start\":1783488222987,\"end\":1783488222987}}}\n141: {\"type\":\"step_start\",\"timestamp\":1783488224142,\"sessionID\":\"ses_0bfd72ffbffeOJIQWH3C696a5x\",\"part\":{\"id\":\"prt_f402e9b8d001aQzIYPmM0GtYvF\",\"messageID\":\"msg_f402e971f001UXcy1OUZrN6IvJ\",\"sessionID\":\"ses_0bfd72ffbffeOJIQWH3C696a5x\",\"snapshot\":\"9cb9852d8bfcfe7abb619e79af6e4ea65e914cef\",\"type\":\"step-start\"}}\n142: {\"type\":\"text\",\"timestamp\":1783488235486,\"sessionID\":\"ses_0bfd72ffbffeOJIQWH3C696a5x\",\"part\":{\"id\":\"prt_f402ec3660010c4Mi30dPBA6uD\",\"messageID\":\"msg_f402e971f001UXcy1OUZrN6IvJ\",\"sessionID\":\"ses_0bfd72ffbffeOJIQWH3C696a5x\",\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"Continuing within the established artifact boundary: `.opencode/specs/system-deep-loop/052-deep-loop-unification/001-reference-research/research/lineages/gpt55-fast-10`. I’ll first re-anchor on the local files/state, then write only lineage-local deep-research artifacts and verify the lineage output.\",\"time\":{\"start\":1783488234342,\"end\":1783488235484},\"metadata\":{\"openai\":{\"itemId\":\"msg_0eb9ba0837705a91016a4ddeea584c8191961fe444e88b5e11\",\"phase\":\"commentary\"}}}}\n\n(Output capped at 50 KB. Showing lines 102-142. Use offset=143 to continue.)\n</content>","metadata":{"preview":"{\"type\":\"tool_use\",\"timestamp\":1783488095641,\"sessionID\":\"ses_0bfd72ffbffeOJIQWH3C696a5x\",\"part\":{\"type\":\"tool\",\"tool\":\"read\",\"callID\":\"call_1ldF2D7ZdPmY3TnAaHFAYoiY\",\"state\":{\"status\":\"error\",\"input\":{\"filePath\":\"/Users/michelkerkmeester/MEGA/Development/Code_Environment/Public/.opencode/skills/system-skill-advisor/mcp_server/advisor-scorer/aliases.ts\",\"offset\":1,\"limit\":220},\"error\":\"File not found: /Users/michelkerkmeester/MEGA/Development/Code_Environment/Public/.opencode/skills/system-skill-advisor/mcp_server/advisor-scorer/aliases.ts\",\"time\":{\"start\":1783488095639,\"end\":1783488095640}},\"metadata\":{\"openai\":{\"itemId\":\"fc_078718e1cef7b346016a4dde5f86508191825bb4fdefb2e682\"}},\"id\":\"prt_f402ca58e001gxQON1jOltIT6g\",\"sessionID\":\"ses_0bfd72ffbffeOJIQWH3C696a5x\",\"messageID\":\"msg_f402c8001001AlIVs7PYaxdrb7\"}}\n{\"type\":\"tool_use\",\"timestamp\":1783488098145,\"sessionID\":\"ses_0bfd72ffbffeOJIQWH3C696a5x\",\"part\":{\"type\":\"tool\",\"tool\":\"read\",\"callID\":\"call_a0pr25ZBVhVGfeBfLNdex8eW\",\"state\":{\"status\":\"error\",\"input\":{\"filePath\":\"/Users/michelkerkmeester/MEGA/Development/Code_Environment/Public/.opencode/skills/system-skill-advisor/mcp_server/advisor-scorer/explicit.ts\",\"offset\":1,\"limit\":220},\"error