\",\"part\":{\"type\":\"tool\",\"tool\":\"read\",\"callID\":\"call_oekR98uSsGHx30zftoEt55XY\",\"state\":{\"status\":\"completed\",\"input\":{\"filePath\":\"/Users/michelkerkmeester/MEGA/Development/Code_Environment/Public/.opencode/skills/system-skill-advisor/mcp_server/scripts/routing-accuracy/labeled-prompts.jsonl\",\"offset\":1,\"limit\":160},\"output\":\"<path>/Users/michelkerkmeester/MEGA/Development/Code_Environment/Public/.opencode/skills/system-skill-advisor/mcp_server/scripts/routing-accuracy/labeled-prompts.jsonl</path>\\n<type>file</type>\\n<content>\\n1: {\\\"id\\\":\\\"rr-iter2-001\\\",\\\"bucket\\\":\\\"true_write\\\",\\\"source_type\\\":\\\"synthetic-realistic\\\",\\\"prompt\\\":\\\"Implement a negative-trigger whitelist in `gate-3-classifier.ts` and run the targeted tests.\\\",\\\"gate3_triggers\\\":\\\"yes\\\",\\\"gate3_reason_category\\\":\\\"file_write\\\",\\\"skill_top_1\\\":\\\"sk-code\\\",\\\"skill_correct\\\":\\\"yes\\\",\\\"notes\\\":\\\"clear code edit request\\\"}\\n2: {\\\"id\\\":\\\"rr-iter2-002\\\",\\\"bucket\\\":\\\"true_write\\\",\\\"source_type\\\":\\\"synthetic-realistic\\\",\\\"prompt\\\":\\\"Edit the routing phase README to document the new corpus file layout.\\\",\\\"gate3_triggers\\\":\\\"yes\\\",\\\"gate3_reason_category\\\":\\\"file_write\\\",\\\"skill_top_1\\\":\\\"sk-doc\\\",\\\"skill_correct\\\":\\\"yes\\\",\\\"notes\\\":\\\"direct documentation write\\\"}\\n3: {\\\"id\\\":\\\"rr-iter2-003\\\",\\\"bucket\\\":\\\"true_write\\\",\\\"source_type\\\":\\\"synthetic-realistic\\\",\\\"prompt\\\":\\\"Add a `corpus/` subdirectory under the routing-accuracy phase and create a starter `labeled-prompts.jsonl`.\\\",\\\"gate3_triggers\\\":\\\"yes\\\",\\\"gate3_reason_category\\\":\\\"file_write\\\",\\\"skill_top_1\\\":\\\"system-spec-kit\\\",\\\"skill_correct\\\":\\\"yes\\\",\\\"notes\\\":\\\"packet-local artifact creation\\\"}\\n4: {\\\"id\\\":\\\"rr-iter2-004\\\",\\\"bucket\\\":\\\"true_write\\\",\\\"source_type\\\":\\\"synthetic-realistic\\\",\\\"prompt\\\":\\\"Refactor `skill_advisor.py` to surface raw ambiguity counts in debug output.\\\",\\\"gate3_triggers\\\":\\\"yes\\\",\\\"gate3_reason_category\\\":\\\"file_write\\\",\\\"skill_top_1\\\":\\\"sk-cod... (line truncated to 2000 chars)\n{\"type\":\"tool_use\",\"timestamp\":1783488128463,\"sessionID\":\"ses_0bfd72ffbffeOJIQWH3C696a5x\",\"part\":{\"type\":\"tool\",\"tool\":\"read\",\"callID\":\"call_XR9Ard7V2e9pOvWmLRzWkU8K\",\"state\":{\"status\":\"completed\",\"input\":{\"filePath\":\"/Users/michelkerkmeester/MEGA/Development/Code_Environment/Public/.opencode/skills/deep-loop-workflows/mode-registry.json\",\"offset\":1,\"limit\":260},\"output\":\"<path>/Users/michelkerkmeester/MEGA/Development/Code_Environment/Public/.opencode/skills/deep-loop-workflows/mode-registry.json</path>\\n<type>file</type>\\n<content>\\n1: {\\n2:   \\\"skill\\\": \\\"deep-loop-workflows\\\",\\n3:   \\\"version\\\": \\\"1.1.0.0\\\",\\n4:   \\\"description\\\": \\\"Declarative mode registry: the single source of truth for the three-tier discriminator (workflowMode/runtimeLoopType/backendKind) PLUS the advisorRouting projection. The advisor keeps its hardcoded projection maps (Python DEEP_ROUTING_MODE_BY_KEY, TypeScript DEEP_MODE_BY_CANONICAL) in sync with this registry via a CI drift-guard test (maps == registry projection); the advisor does NOT read this file at runtime, which avoids cross-skill import coupling on the advisor hot path.\\\",\\n5:   \\\"discriminator\\\": {\\n6:     \\\"workflowMode\\\": \\\"Public command/advisor/mode key. Stable identity used in commands, advisor aliases, and this registry. Carried by every mode.\\\",\\n7:     \\\"runtimeLoopType\\\": \\\"The graph-backed convergence loop key consumed by deep-loop-runtime/scripts/convergence.cjs. Validated against exactly research|review|council. Explicit null for improvement-host and external-adapter modes; NEVER inferred from workflowMode.\\\",\\n8:     \\\"backendKind\\\": \\\"Which backend actually runs the mode: runtime-loop-type (deep-loop-runtime convergence), improvement-host (deep-improvement/scripts/shared/loop-host.cjs --mode), or external-adapter (loop owned by external packaging).\\\"\\n9:   },\\n10:   \\\"advisorRoutingContract\\\": {\\n11:     \\\"routingClass\\\": \\\"How the advisor finds the mode. 'lexical' = weighted-regex scoring in skill_advisor.py AND... (line truncated to 2000 chars)\n{\"type\":\"tool_use\",\"timestamp\":1783488128639,\"sessionID\":\"ses_0bfd72ffbffeOJIQWH3C696a5x\",\"part\":{\"type\":\"tool\",\"tool\":\"read\",\"callID\":\"call_k6fgv7BTCOSPFC9SkfTbxu34\",\"state\":{\"status\":\"completed\",\"input\":{\"filePath\":\"/Users/michelkerkmeester/MEGA/Development/Code_Environment/Public/.opencode/skills/deep-loop-workflows/hub-router.json\",\"offset\":1,\"limit\":160},\"output\":\"<path>/Users/michelkerkmeester/MEGA/Development/Code_Environment/Public/.opencode/skills/deep-loop-workflows/hub-router.json</path>\\n<type>file</type>\\n<content>\\n1: {\\n2:   \\\"skill\\\": \\\"deep-loop-workflows\\\",\\n3:   \\\"version\\\": \\\"1.1.0.0\\\",\\n4:   \\\"routerPolicy\\\": {\\n5:     \\\"defaultMode\\\": \\\"research\\\",\\n6:     \\\"ambiguityDelta\\\": 1,\\n7:     \\\"tieBreak\\\": [\\\"research\\\", \\\"review\\\", \\\"ai-council\\\", \\\"agent-improvement\\\", \\\"model-benchmark\\\", \\\"skill-benchmark\\\", \\\"ai-system-improvement\\\"],\\n8:     \\\"outcomes\\\": {\\n9:       \\\"single\\\": \\\"one dominant deep-loop intent routes to one mode\\\",\\n10:       \\\"orderedBundle\\\": \\\"clearly separate deep-loop intents route to an ordered mode list\\\",\\n11:       \\\"defer\\\": \\\"unclear or contradictory deep-loop intent asks for disambiguation\\\"\\n12:     },\\n13:     \\\"defaultResource\\\": [\\\"README.md\\\"]\\n14:   },\\n15:   \\\"routerSignals\\\": {\\n16:     \\\"research\\\": {\\n17:       \\\"weight\\\": 4,\\n18:       \\\"classes\\\": [\\\"research-aliases\\\", \\\"hub-identity\\\"],\\n19:       \\\"resources\\\": [\\\"deep-research/SKILL.md\\\"]\\n20:     },\\n21:     \\\"review\\\": {\\n22:       \\\"weight\\\": 4,\\n23:       \\\"classes\\\": [\\\"review-aliases\\\", \\\"hub-identity\\\"],\\n24:       \\\"resources\\\": [\\\"deep-review/SKILL.md\\\"]\\n25:     },\\n26:     \\\"ai-council\\\": {\\n27:       \\\"weight\\\": 4,\\n28:       \\\"classes\\\": [\\\"ai-council-aliases\\\", \\\"hub-identity\\\"],\\n29:       \\\"resources\\\": [\\\"deep-ai-council/SKILL.md\\\"]\\n30:     },\\n31:     \\\"agent-improvement\\\": {\\n32:       \\\"weight\\\": 4,\\n33:       \\\"classes\\\": [\\\"agent-improvement-aliases\\\", \\\"hub-identity\\\"],\\n34:       \\\"resources\\\": [\\\"deep-improvement/SKILL.md\\\"]... (line truncated to 2000 chars)\n{\"type\":\"tool_use\",\"timestamp\":1783488128640,\"sessionID\":\"ses_0bfd72ffbffeOJIQWH3C696a5x\",\"part\":{\"type\":\"tool\",\"tool\":\"read\",\"callID\":\"call_DfwaY9MlDZMPvPWO4PTxkIs1\",\"state\":{\"status\":\"completed\",\"input\":{\"filePath\":\"/Users/michelkerkmeester/MEGA/Development/Code_Environment/Public/.opencode/skills/deep-loop-workflows/description.json\",\"offset\":1,\"limit\":200},\"output\":\"<path>/Users/michelkerkmeester/MEGA/Development/Code_Environment/Public/.opencode/skills/deep-loop-workflows/description.json</path>\\n<type>file</type>\\n<content>\\n1: {\\n2:   \\\"name\\\": \\\"deep-loop-workflows\\\",\\n3:   \\\"description\\\": \\\"Unified deep-loop workflow parent hub: the single advisor-routable home for active deep-loop personas, routing to seven modes across four workflow families over the shared deep-loop-runtime backend. research (outward web+code iterative investigation → research/ artifacts), review (iterative review loop → P0/P1/P2 findings + verdict), ai-council (multi-seat planning deliberation → ai-council/ artifacts), and four improvement lanes on the deep-improvement packet (agent-improvement, model-benchmark, skill-benchmark, ai-system-improvement). The hub holds no per-mode convergence, state, or synthesis logic; each mode keeps its own contract in its packet and is reachable via its /deep:* command and native agent.\\\",\\n4:   \\\"version\\\": \\\"1.1.0.0\\\",\\n5:   \\\"importance_tier\\\": \\\"high\\\",\\n6:   \\\"keywords\\\": [\\n7:     \\\"deep-loop-workflows\\\",\\n8:     \\\"deep-loop\\\",\\n9:     \\\"deep-research\\\",\\n10:     \\\"deep-review\\\",\\n11:     \\\"deep-ai-council\\\",\\n12:     \\\"deep-improvement\\\",\\n13:     \\\"autoresearch\\\",\\n14:     \\\"iterative-research\\\",\\n15:     \\\"research-convergence\\\",\\n16:     \\\"review-loop\\\",\\n17:     \\\"severity-findings\\\",\\n18:     \\\"P0-P1-P2\\\",\\n19:     \\\"release-readiness\\\",\\n20:     \\\"ai-council\\\",\\n21:     \\\"council-deliberation\\\",\\n22:     \\\"multi-seat-planning\\\",\\n23:     \\\"agent-improvement\\\",\\n24:     \\\"model-benchmark\\\",\\n25:     \\\"skill-benchmark\\\",\\n26:     \\\"non-dev-... (line truncated to 2000 chars)\n{\"type\":\"tool_use\",\"timestamp\":1783488128644,\"sessionID\":\"ses_0bfd72ffbffeOJIQWH3C696a5x\",\"part\":{\"type\":\"tool\",\"tool\":\"read\",\"callID\":\"call_O0BWm9fW47Lxt8ONMFlFArl5\",\"state\":{\"status\":\"error\",\"input\":{\"filePath\":\"/Users/michelkerkmeester/MEGA/Development/Code_Environment/Public/.opencode/skills/deep-loop-runtime/description.json\",\"offset\":1,\"limit\":200},\"error\":\"File not found: /Users/michelkerkmeester/MEGA/Development/Code_Environment/Public/.opencode/skills/deep-loop-runtime/description.json\",\"time\":{\"start\":1783488128643,\"end\":1783488128644}},\"metadata\":{\"openai\":{\"itemId\":\"fc_01709570d2949561016a4dde8052448191a52fcf09125404d8\"}},\"id\":\"prt_f402d267b001yjkTbWXtMJJ50E\",\"sessionID\":\"ses_0bfd72ffbffeOJIQWH3C696a5x\",\"messageID\":\"msg_f402cfc11001beoLe363U2oZVH\"}}\n{\"type\":\"step_finish\",\"timestamp\":1783488128970,\"sessionID\":\"ses_0bfd72ffbffeOJIQWH3C696a5x\",\"part\":{\"id\":\"prt_f402d27c8001SAepYmDIExBB9V\",\"reason\":\"tool-calls\",\"snapshot\"