{"type":"text","timestamp":1783489615682,"sessionID":"ses_0bfc4afb7ffeA8X2g5OnaG20YL","part":{"id":"prt_f404391070019cGOIkXLiNRhfM","messageID":"msg_f40435ee5001G1lyRJYIhz4cNW","sessionID":"ses_0bfc4afb7ffeA8X2g5OnaG20YL","type":"text","text":"## Goal\n- Execute detached deep-research fan-out lineage `gpt55-fast-10` for system-deep-loop merge validation and finish with `FANOUT_LINEAGE_COMPLETE:gpt55-fast-10`.\n\n## Constraints & Preferences\n- Write outputs only under `.opencode/specs/system-deep-loop/052-deep-loop-unification/001-reference-research/research/lineages/gpt55-fast-10`.\n- Do not run `resolveArtifactRoot`; bind `artifact_dir` directly to `config.fanout_lineage_artifact_dir`.\n- Run `phase_init`, `phase_main_loop` to convergence or 10 iterations, and `phase_synthesis`.\n- Executor: `cli-opencode model=openai/gpt-5.5-fast`.\n- Loop type: `research`; stop policy: `convergence`; max iterations: `10`.\n- Final response must be exactly: `FANOUT_LINEAGE_COMPLETE:gpt55-fast-10`.\n\n## Progress\n### Done\n- Read `.opencode/skills/deep-loop-workflows/deep-research/SKILL.md`.\n- Loaded deep-research references for loop protocol, state, outputs, convergence, reducer registry, spec check, and capability matrix.\n- Inspected target lineage directory; found scaffold only plus `logs/fanout-lineage.out`, no canonical state/config/iteration artifacts.\n- Memory trigger lookup with detached `session_id` failed: `E_SESSION_SCOPE`; retried without session and found no matching trigger phrases.\n- Gathered evidence from specs, runtime scripts, command routes, agents, advisor code, and model profiles.\n- Added lineage artifacts:\n  - `deep-research-config.json`\n  - `deep-research-state.jsonl`\n  - `deep-research-strategy.md`\n  - `deep-research-findings-registry.json`\n  - `deep-research-dashboard.md`\n  - `resource-map.md`\n  - `research.md`\n\n### In Progress\n- Need create/verify per-iteration narrative files and delta files.\n\n### Blocked\n- `(none)`\n\n## Key Decisions\n- Treated existing lineage directory as partial fresh packet because only scaffold dirs and `logs/fanout-lineage.out` existed.\n- Skipped spec write-back and memory save because detached lineage boundary forbids writes outside `gpt55-fast-10`.\n- Recorded convergence after 10 iterations in JSONL with `stopReason: converged`.\n- Core recommendation recorded: proceed with 002/003 guardrails; keep 004 fallback-router wiring optional unless operator opts in.\n\n## Next Steps\n- Add `iterations/iteration-001.md` through `iterations/iteration-010.md`.\n- Add matching per-iteration delta files under `deltas/`.\n- Validate JSON in `deep-research-config.json`, `deep-research-state.jsonl`, and `deep-research-findings-registry.json`.\n- Ensure no required artifact is missing for `verify-iteration.cjs`.\n- Update todo state if tools remain available.\n- Output `FANOUT_LINEAGE_COMPLETE:gpt55-fast-10`.\n\n## Critical Context\n- Target artifact dir: `.opencode/specs/system-deep-loop/052-deep-loop-unification/001-reference-research/research/lineages/gpt55-fast-10`.\n- Detached lineage session id: `fanout-gpt55-fast-10-1783486518892-2qss01`.\n- Important findings:\n  - `runtime/` must remain infrastructure, not a `workflowMode`.\n  - Path repair is asymmetric: forward references keep hop count; reverse references move one hop nearer.\n  - `system-spec-kit` tooling-borrow is load-bearing.\n  - Advisor migration is highest-risk due generated projection/hash plus hand-authored scorer constants.\n  - `fallback-router.ts` has resolver/guards but no fanout caller; GLM→MiMo fallback is optional feature scope.\n- Existing `logs/fanout-lineage.out` includes prior attempt context but no canonical state before current writes.\n\n## Relevant Files\n- `.opencode/skills/deep-loop-workflows/deep-research/SKILL.md`: workflow contract.\n- `.opencode/commands/deep/assets/deep_research_auto.yaml`: YAML loop source.\n- `.opencode/specs/system-deep-loop/052-deep-loop-unification/001-reference-research/research/lineages/gpt55-fast-10`: detached lineage root.\n- `.opencode/specs/system-deep-loop/052-deep-loop-unification/001-reference-research/research/lineages/gpt55-fast-10/deep-research-state.jsonl`: append-only state log with 10 iteration records.\n- `.opencode/specs/system-deep-loop/052-deep-loop-unification/001-reference-research/research/lineages/gpt55-fast-10/research.md`: synthesis output.\n- `.opencode/specs/system-deep-loop/052-deep-loop-unification/001-reference-research/research/lineages/gpt55-fast-10/iterations`: still needs iteration markdown files.\n- `.opencode/specs/system-deep-loop/052-deep-loop-unification/001-reference-research/research/lineages/gpt55-fast-10/deltas`: still needs delta files.","time":{"start":1783489597703,"end":1783489615677},"metadata":{"openai":{"itemId":"msg_06108a93ee9747d1016a4de43db244819188ca74bd7ab3c837","phase":"final_answer"}}}}
