phases.\n35: \n36: ## Blocked Stops\n37: \n38: None.\n39: \n40: ## Graph Convergence\n41: \n42: No graph events were emitted by this lineage; graph gates are not applicable.\n43: \n44: ## Next Focus\n45: \n46: Proceed with 002 and 003 as staged; decide 004 fallback-router wiring separately.\n47: \n48: ## Boundary Notes\n49: \n50: Spec write-back, memory save, and git staging were skipped because the detached lineage prompt explicitly forbids writes outside the lineage directory.\n\n(End of file - total 50 lines)\n</content>","metadata":{"preview":"# Deep Research Dashboard - gpt55-fast-10\n\nAuto-generated lineage summary from `deep-research-state.jsonl`, registry, and strategy.\n\n## Iteration Table\n\n| Run | Focus | newInfoRatio | Findings | Status |\n|-----|-------|--------------|----------|--------|\n| 1 | Charter/scope | 1.00 | 4 | complete |\n| 2 | Structural layout | 0.82 | 4 | complete |\n| 3 | Path coupling | 0.76 | 5 | complete |\n| 4 | Tooling-borrow | 0.70 | 5 | complete |\n| 5 | Commands/agents | 0.66 | 5 | complete |\n| 6 | Advisor surfaces | 0.62 | 6 | complete |\n| 7 | Fallback router caller | 0.52 | 5 | complete |\n| 8 | GLM/MiMo model facts | 0.35 | 4 | complete |\n| 9 | 003 gates | 0.18 | 4 | complete |\n| 10 | Convergence/recommendation | 0.06 | 4 | complete |\n\n## Question Status","truncated":false,"loaded":[],"display":{"type":"file","path":"/Users/michelkerkmeester/MEGA/Development/Code_Environment/Public/.opencode/specs/system-deep-loop/052-deep-loop-unification/001-reference-research/research/lineages/gpt55-fast-10/deep-research-dashboard.md","text":"# Deep Research Dashboard - gpt55-fast-10\n\nAuto-generated lineage summary from `deep-research-state.jsonl`, registry, and strategy.\n\n## Iteration Table\n\n| Run | Focus | newInfoRatio | Findings | Status |\n|-----|-------|--------------|----------|--------|\n| 1 | Charter/scope | 1.00 | 4 | complete |\n| 2 | Structural layout | 0.82 | 4 | complete |\n| 3 | Path coupling | 0.76 | 5 | complete |\n| 4 | Tooling-borrow | 0.70 | 5 | complete |\n| 5 | Commands/agents | 0.66 | 5 | complete |\n| 6 | Advisor surfaces | 0.62 | 6 | complete |\n| 7 | Fallback router caller | 0.52 | 5 | complete |\n| 8 | GLM/MiMo model facts | 0.35 | 4 | complete |\n| 9 | 003 gates | 0.18 | 4 | complete |\n| 10 | Convergence/recommendation | 0.06 | 4 | complete |\n\n## Question Status\n\n5/5 answered.\n\n## Convergence Trend\n\nTrend: `1.00 -> 0.82 -> 0.76 -> 0.70 -> 0.66 -> 0.62 -> 0.52 -> 0.35 -> 0.18 -> 0.06`.\n\nFinal signals: rolling average `0.196`, entropy coverage `1.0`, composite stop score `0.70`; legal stop gates passed.\n\n## Dead Ends\n\n- Naive global replace.\n- Runtime as a mode-registry entry.\n- Silent GLM-to-MiMo fallback bundled into mandatory merge phases.\n\n## Blocked Stops\n\nNone.\n\n## Graph Convergence\n\nNo graph events were emitted by this lineage; graph gates are not applicable.\n\n## Next Focus\n\nProceed with 002 and 003 as staged; decide 004 fallback-router wiring separately.\n\n## Boundary Notes\n\nSpec write-back, memory save, and git staging were skipped because the detached lineage prompt explicitly forbids writes outside the lineage directory.","lineStart":1,"lineEnd":50,"totalLines":50,"truncated":false}},"title":".opencode/specs/system-deep-loop/052-deep-loop-unification/001-reference-research/research/lineages/gpt55-fast-10/deep-research-dashboard.md","time":{"start":1783489706603,"end":1783489706613}},"metadata":{"openai":{"itemId":"fc_05252c6e66f2eed4016a4de4aa866c8191bd4283abb440e97c"}},"id":"prt_f40453a60001nrWiovAn8rY1zC","sessionID":"ses_0bfc4afb7ffeA8X2g5OnaG20YL","messageID":"msg_f40450e8d00117QbEvGzbc3uCU"}}
