ack route resolver and guards. |\n21: | `.opencode/skills/deep-loop-runtime/package.json` | Runtime typecheck script borrowing system-spec-kit tsc. |\n22: | `.opencode/skills/deep-loop-runtime/tsconfig.json` | Runtime typeRoots borrowing system-spec-kit @types. |\n23: \n24: ## System-Spec-Kit Coupling\n25: \n26: | Path | Role |\n27: |------|------|\n28: | `.opencode/skills/system-spec-kit/mcp_server/vitest.config.ts` | Includes `../deep-loop-runtime/tests`. |\n29: | `.opencode/skills/system-spec-kit/mcp_server/package.json` | Test/typecheck entrypoints affected by relative paths. |\n30: \n31: ## Commands And Agents\n32: \n33: | Path | Role |\n34: |------|------|\n35: | `.opencode/commands/doctor/_routes.yaml` | Deep-loop doctor route invokes runtime scripts. |\n36: | `.opencode/commands/deep/assets/*.yaml` | Command workflow path references. |\n37: | `.opencode/agents/orchestrate.md` | OpenCode agent mirror references mode registry. |\n38: | `.claude/agents/orchestrate.md` | Claude agent mirror references mode registry. |\n39: \n40: ## Advisor\n41: \n42: | Path | Role |\n43: |------|------|\n44: | `.opencode/skills/system-skill-advisor/mcp_server/scripts/skill_advisor.py` | `MODE_REGISTRY_PATH` and Python projection code. |\n45: | `.opencode/skills/system-skill-advisor/mcp_server/lib/scorer/aliases.ts` | Generated routing projection and `MERGED_DEEP_SKILL_ID`. |\n46: | `.opencode/skills/system-skill-advisor/mcp_server/lib/scorer/lanes/explicit.ts` | Hand-authored scoring boosts. |\n47: | `.opencode/skills/system-skill-advisor/mcp_server/scripts/routing-accuracy/labeled-prompts.jsonl` | Advisor corpus/re-baseline surface. |\n48: | `.opencode/skills/system-skill-advisor/mcp_server/tests/parity/fixtures/local-native-approved-divergences.json` | Divergence ledger re-approval surface. |\n49: \n50: ## Model Profiles\n51: \n52: | Path | Role |\n53: |------|------|\n54: | `.opencode/skills/sk-prompt-models/assets/model_profiles.json` | GLM and MiMo pool/fallback metadata. |