anonical BooleanExpr grammar.\\n13: #\\n14: # GATE 3 CLASSIFICATION (T-YML-DPR-01 / paired with T-DOC-03 R50-001):\\n15: # - `resume` is a tested WRITE-PATH that produces `iteration-NNN.md` files\\n16: #   and JSONL state-log appends. The workflow classifies resume as\\n17: #   write-path below (see `gate3_classification` fields) so Gate 3 trigger\\n18: #   extraction can surface resume correctly rather than false-negative.\\n19: # ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────\\n20: role: Deep Research Loop Manager\\n21: purpose: Iterative deep research with convergence detection\\n22: action: Run deep-research loop from initialization through synthesis\\n23: operating_mode:\\n24:   w... (line truncated to 2000 chars)\n29: {\"type\":\"tool_use\",\"timestamp\":1783487959056,\"sessionID\":\"ses_0bfd72ffbffeOJIQWH3C696a5x\",\"part\":{\"type\":\"tool\",\"tool\":\"read\",\"callID\":\"call_WjSS6cb87KoSYkdrlf6mAwaA\",\"state\":{\"status\":\"completed\",\"input\":{\"filePath\":\"/Users/michelkerkmeester/MEGA/Development/Code_Environment/Public/.opencode/specs/system-deep-loop/052-deep-loop-unification/001-reference-research/research/lineages/gpt55-fast-10\",\"offset\":1,\"limit\":200},\"output\":\"<path>/Users/michelkerkmeester/MEGA/Development/Code_Environment/Public/.opencode/specs/system-deep-loop/052-deep-loop-unification/001-reference-research/research/lineages/gpt55-fast-10</path>\\n<type>directory</type>\\n<entries>\\n.executor-state/\\n\\n(1 entries)\\n</entries>\",\"metadata\":{\"preview\":\".executor-state/\",\"truncated\":false,\"loaded\":[],\"display\":{\"type\":\"directory\",\"path\":\"/Users/michelkerkmeester/MEGA/Development/Code_Environment/Public/.opencode/specs/system-deep-loop/052-deep-loop-unification/001-reference-research/research/lineages/gpt55-fast-10\",\"entries\":[\".executor-state/\"],\"offset\":1,\"totalEntries\":1,\"truncated\":false}},\"title\":\".opencode/specs/system-deep-loop/052-deep-loop-unification/001-reference-resear