:{\"itemId\":\"msg_07526b59faa59b89016a4dddcfda1c819191570ec468ca98e4\",\"phase\":\"commentary\"}}}}\n{\"type\":\"tool_use\",\"timestamp\":1783487959034,\"sessionID\":\"ses_0bfd72ffbffeOJIQWH3C696a5x\",\"part\":{\"type\":\"tool\",\"tool\":\"read\",\"callID\":\"call_CZHOowiJHvjo53X3nVyxhrI7\",\"state\":{\"status\":\"completed\",\"input\":{\"filePath\":\"/Users/michelkerkmeester/MEGA/Development/Code_Environment/Public/.opencode/commands/deep/research.md\",\"offset\":1,\"limit\":2000},\"output\":\"<path>/Users/michelkerkmeester/MEGA/Development/Code_Environment/Public/.opencode/commands/deep/research.md</path>\\n<type>file</type>\\n<content>\\n1: ---\\n2: description: Autonomous deep-research loop: iterative investigation with convergence detection. Modes :auto, :confirm.\\n3: argument-hint: \\\"<topic> [:auto|:confirm] [--max-iterations=N] [--convergence=N] [--lineage-timeout-hours=N] [--stop-policy=convergence|max-iterations] [--dry-run] [--executor=<type> [--model=X] [--config-dir=PATH] [--count=N] [--label=X] ...] [--executors=<json>] [--concurrency=N] (:auto supports PRE-BOUND SETUP ANSWERS: prompt-body block for non-interactive setup)\\\"\\n4: allowed-tools: Read, Write, Edit, Bash, Grep, Glob, Task, WebFetch, mcp__mk_spec_memory__memory_context, mcp__mk_spec_memory__memory_search, mcp__mk_code_index__code_graph_query, mcp__mk_code_index__code_graph_context\\n5: ---\\n6: \\n7: # Deep Start Research Loop\\n8: \\n9: !`node .opencode/skills/deep-loop-runtime/scripts/render-command-contract.cjs --command deep/research -- '$ARGUMENTS'`\\n\\n(End of file - total 9 lines)\\n</content>\",\"metadata\":{\"preview\":\"---\\ndescription: Autonomous deep-research loop: iterative investigation with convergence detection. Modes :auto, :confirm.\\nargument-hint: \\\"<topic> [:auto|:confirm] [--max-iterations=N] [--convergence=N] [--lineage-timeout-hours=N] [--stop-policy=convergence|max-iterations] [--dry-run] [--executor=<type> [--model=X] [--config-dir=PATH] [--count=N] [--label=X] ...] [--executors=<json>] [--concurrency=N] (:auto supports PRE-BOUND SETUP ANSWERS: prompt-body block for non-interactive setup)\\\"\\nallowed-tools: Read, Write, Edit,... (line truncated to 2000 chars)\n{\"type\":\"tool_use\",\"timestamp\":1783487959056,\"sessionID\":\"ses_0bfd72ffbffeOJIQWH3C696a5x\",\"part\":{\"type\":\"tool\",\"tool\":\"read\",\"callID\":\"call_BDloeAZY53qVWVOGDFlYK6jg\",\"state\":{\"status\":\"completed\",\"input\":{\"filePath\":\"/Users/michelkerkmeester/MEGA/Development/Code_Environment/Public/.opencode/commands/deep/assets/deep_research_auto.yaml\",\"offset\":1,\"limit\":4000},\"output\":\"<path>/Users/michelkerkmeester/MEGA/Development/Code_Environment/Public/.opencode/commands/deep/assets/deep_research_auto.yaml</path>\\n<type>file</type>\\n<content>\\n1: # ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────\\n2: # DEEP RESEARCH: AUTONOMOUS DEEP RESEARCH LOOP (AUTO MODE)\\n3: # ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────\\n4: # YAML PREDICATE GRAMMAR CONTRACT (S7 / M11):\\n5: # - This asset does not currently use typed BooleanExpr predicates under\\n6: #   `when:`; flow control is branch-label-driven (`on_resume`, `on_fresh`,\\n7: #   `on_restart`, etc.). Retain the existing shape.\\n8: # - `after:` carries prose timing / narrative notes if needed; `when:` in\\n9: #   this file is reserved for future typed predicates and must NOT carry\\n10: #   free-form narrative prose.\\n11: # - See `.opencode/skills/system-spec-kit/shared/predicates/boolean-expr.ts`\\n12: #   for the canonical BooleanExpr grammar.\\n13: #\\n14: # GATE 3 CLASSIFICATION (T-YML-DPR-01 / paired with T-DOC-03 R50-001):\\n15: # - `resume` is a tested WRITE-PATH that produces `iteration-NNN.md` files\\n16: #   and JSONL state-log appends. The workflow classifies resume as\\n17: #   write-path below (see `gate3_classification` fields) so Gate 3 trigger\\n18: #   extraction can surface resume correctly rather than false-negative.\\n19