idirectional path-coupling rules correct?\"],\"answeredQuestions\":[\"The forward and reverse directions require different repairs, not one global substitution.\"],\"keyFindings\":[{\"id\":\"finding-asymmetric-coupling\",\"title\":\"Path repair is intentionally asymmetric\",\"sources\":[\".opencode/specs/system-deep-loop/052-deep-loop-unification/002-hub-rename-and-runtime-nesting/spec.md:58\",\".opencode/specs/system-deep-loop/052-deep-loop-unification/002-hub-rename-and-runtime-nesting/spec.md:72\",\".opencode/specs/system-deep-loop/052-deep-loop-unification/002-hub-rename-and-runtime-nesting/spec.md:173\",\".opencode/specs/system-deep-loop/052-deep-loop-unification/002-hub-rename-and-runtime-nesting/spec.md:174\"]}],\"durationMs\":118000,\"timestamp\":\"2026-07-08T05:41:43Z\",\"sessionId\":\"fanout-gpt55-fast-10-1783486518892-2qss01\",\"generation\":1}\n","additions":1,"deletions":0},{"filePath":"/Users/michelkerkmeester/MEGA/Development/Code_Environment/Public/.opencode/specs/system-deep-loop/052-deep-loop-unification/001-reference-research/research/lineages/gpt55-fast-10/deltas/iter-004.jsonl","relativePath":".opencode/specs/system-deep-loop/052-deep-loop-unification/001-reference-research/research/lineages/gpt55-fast-10/deltas/iter-004.jsonl","type":"add","patch":"Index: /Users/michelkerkmeester/MEGA/Development/Code_Environment/Public/.opencode/specs/system-deep-loop/052-deep-loop-unification/001-reference-research/research/lineages/gpt55-fast-10/deltas/iter-004.jsonl\n===================================================================\n--- /Users/michelkerkmeester/MEGA/Development/Code_Environment/Public/.opencode/specs/system-deep-loop/052-deep-loop-unification/001-reference-research/research/lineages/gpt55-fast-10/deltas/iter-004.jsonl\n+++ /Users/michelkerkmeester/MEGA/Development/Code_Environment/Public/.opencode/specs/system-deep-loop/052-deep-loop-unification/001-reference-research/research/lineages/gpt55-fast-10/deltas/iter-004.jsonl\n@@ -0,0 +1,1 @@\